</P>
<P>
   Museum officials took the settlement more quietly. ``We're
stronger,'' said Robert S. Rubin, the chairman.
</P>
<P>
   _ By ALAN FEUER
</P>
<P>
   OPEC Votes to Raise Oil Production
</P>
