   POLITICS
</P>
<P>
   GORE-SCANDAL _ Al Gore this week said he is ``an imperfect
messenger'' for campaign finance reform. As the campaign continues,
those imperfections _ particulary the Buddhist temple visit and the
fundraising calls from the White House _will come under closer
scrutiny. We take a detailed look at those two events _ who said
what, who has been charged, who has been convicted, and what
remains in the investigation of each. (Foskett, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution)
</P>
