<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-04-01 16:24 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4357 &Cx1f; taf-z
u a BC-NY-DOTCOM-RENTS-NYT &LR;      04-01 0899
