hasn't run this high since the Big Red Machine days. But in
reality, what impact will Junior Griffey have on this team, which
looks strong on offense, strong up the middle, weak at the corners.
And, oh, then there's the part of the game called pitching, a huge
question mark. (McCoy, Dayton Daily News). 25. WITH PHOTOS. MOVED
WITH
