   BBN-REDS-BOWDEN _ Reds General Manager Jim Bowden is one of the
brightest in baseball. And the story has been told before, right?
Wrong. We want to know exactly why fate smiles on him so often and
if he's in Cincinnati to stay. (McCoy or McClelland, Dayton Daily
