<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-04-01 18:27 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4384 &Cx1f; taf-z
u s BC-SKATE-WORLD-615&AMP;ADD-N     04-01 0748
