 &HT;    
 &HT;    
 &HT;    MICROSOFT-ANTITRUST _ After four months of negotiation,
settlement talks between Microsoft and the government broke down
Saturday evening, setting up the strong likelihood that the trial
judge will issue his verdict in the long running antitrust case
early next week. 
 
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service   
