<HEADLINE>
OPEN SEASON DECLARED ON DUMB PEOPLE 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
 By E.J. MONTINI 
 c.2000 The Arizona Republic  
(PHOENIX) - Arizona politicians are well aware of how stupid the
majority of you people are. But, being politicians, they've failed
to act on it, at least until last week. That's when your luck ran
out.
